  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个系统上下文图，展示客户端如何访问我们的核心平台。主要参与者是一个外部客户端，通过HTTP调用我们的入口服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。这个入口服务有具体名称吗？另外客户端到入口服务的通信协议是什么，直接HTTP还是经过网关？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "入口服务叫Commander，是系统的核心编排层。客户端流量经过Envoy代理，所以关系可以描述为\"HTTP via Envoy\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Client和Commander System，并标注了HTTP via Envoy的调用关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要画出身份认证部分。客户端在调用API前要先去外部的OIDC提供商做认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "idp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个OIDC提供商是我们系统内部的吗？还是完全外部的第三方服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是外部的，比如Auth0或者企业自建的OIDC服务。我们把它标记为Identity Provider，描述写\"OIDC provider\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Identity Provider作为外部人员角色，并建立了Client到IdP的Authenticate关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "idp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Commander下面会调用两个核心系统：一个是Resource Actor System，负责资源的生命周期管理；另一个是Resource ID System，专门生成唯一ID。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个都是内部系统对吧？Commander调用它们的方式是什么，HTTP还是gRPC？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "都是内部系统。Commander通过内部调用\"Invoke actors\"来驱动Actor系统，向ID系统\"Request IDs\"来获取资源标识。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，已添加Resource Actor System和Resource ID System，以及Commander到两者的调用关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "差点忘了权限控制。Actor系统在执行业务操作前需要查询授权策略，我们用的是Cerbos作为外部PDP。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "actor",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Cerbos是Policy Decision Point的意思吗？这个组件应该标记为外部系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Cerbos PDP是专门做授权决策的外部服务。Actor向它发起\"AuthZ query\"来获取权限判定结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "actor",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Cerbos PDP作为外部系统，并建立了Actor到Cerbos的授权查询关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "actor",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "让我整体看一下。Client通过Envoy访问Commander，同时去IdP认证；Commander调用Actor和ID系统；Actor查询Cerbos授权。流程完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander",
        "idp",
        "actor",
        "resourceId",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下细节：Client到Commander的连线描述是\"HTTP via Envoy\"，Client到IdP是\"Authenticate\"，这两个都没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "commander",
        "idp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外Commander到Actor是\"Invoke actors\"，到ID系统是\"Request IDs\"，Actor到Cerbos是\"AuthZ query\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有关系标注已核对完成。现在图中包含6个元素：Client、Identity Provider、Commander System、Resource Actor System、Resource ID System和Cerbos PDP。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "idp",
        "commander",
        "actor",
        "resourceId",
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Cerbos的描述我再看一下，之前说的是\"Authorization\"，但更准确应该是\"Policy Decision Point\"的缩写PDP，描述改成\"Authorization\"就行，标签保留Cerbos PDP。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cerbos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，已将Cerbos的显示名称修正为\"Cerbos PDP\"，描述保持为\"Authorization\"。",
